Deemos held up a list. He crossed out Land Mine. The names Lightmare and
Time Bomb were already marked out, and Psuedo, Stranato, and Inzola were
left. On additional kills were Etchingar and Dead Weight. Under hidden
kills, where nobody could access except Deemos, was Doom Ice.

"Another succesful kill! Now where to? How about the Alliance base? Stranato
and Inzola are there, they'd be good targets." Deemos said. The Chosen Ones
headed back to the Maximal base to get repaired, for it was their right, and
their right, is always right...

> ::DrillBit::
>
> DrillBit saw everything, he ran up to KitKat, and huged her. He could
> only imagine what was going through her head right now.
> "Oh, god. You did the right thing. They would have tortured her. You
> saved her. What Deemos said, was just to anger you." He said, trying to
> comfort her.
> "I have to go to that pod. I'll be back." He said.
> He then went to the hatch, got out, and ran up to GoldenEye and Dollen.
> "What is the situation? Can he be moved?" He asked.
